dct_title_s: Geological map of the Tent Hills quadrangle, San Luis Obispo, Monterey, Kings & Kern counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle TENT HILLS, CA 1994, DMA 1955 I SW--Series V795."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
